Airports Company South Africa (ACSA) has appointed Dirk Kunz acting CFO. His appointment follows the resignation of Maureen Manyama as ACSA CFO and executive director. &ldquo;Kunz is a chartered accountant with over eight years at ACSA . . . [he] has led a number of key strategic initiatives as group manager of corporate finance,&rdquo; ACSA said in a statement on Thursday.